    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double-VANOS system. The mechanical provenance is impeccable, including a documented rear subframe reinforcement and a refreshed cooling system to ensure thermal efficiency under load. The 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile feedback, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. Every component, from the suspension bushings to the high-compression internals, remains in peak operational state. This is a collector-grade example with a flawless service history and no mechanical compromises.",
